ollapsed%20in%20Baltimore%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20Bayer%20quickly%20received%20an%20alert%20that%20168%20of%20its%20shipments%20would%20be%20affected%20by%20the%20disruption%20in%20the%20port.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20March%202020%2C%20the%20German%20pharmaceutical%20and%20agricultural%20producer%20began%20working%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsupply-chain-tech-startup-fourkites-hungry-for-acquisitions-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFourKites%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20supply-chain-intelligence%20platform%20that%20tracks%20shipments%20and%20provides%20real-time%20visibility%20for%20when%20goods%20will%20be%20delivered%20to%20ports%2C%20warehouses%2C%20manufacturing%20facilities%2C%20and%20stores.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20unfolded%20and%20upended%20the%20international%20supply%20chain%2C%20the%20benefits%20of%20Bayer's%20partnership%20with%20FourKites%20became%20evident.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverything%20is%20about%20expectations%2C%26quot%3B%20Johnny%20Ivanyi%2C%20the%20global%20head%20of%20logistics%20for%20Bayer%20Crop%20Science%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BEven%20if%20we%20don't%20deliver%20on%20time%2C%20your%20customer%20can%20say%2C%20'At%20least%20I%20got%20the%20information%20to%20make%20my%20decision.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBayer%20Crop%20Science%20uses%20FourKites%20for%20shipments%20across%20more%20than%2065%20countries%2C%20with%20FourKites%20tracking%20the%20majority%20of%20Bayer's%20containers%20as%20they%20move%20from%20port%20to%20port.%20FourKites%20can%20also%20track%20raw%20materials%20as%20they%20move%20along%20oceans%2C%20railways%2C%20roads%2C%20and%20air%2C%20from%20fields%20to%20ports%20to%20trucks%20and%20then%20from%20manufacturing%20facilities%20and%20warehouses%20to%20final%20delivery%20on%20a%20farm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20complexity%2C%26quot%3B%20Ivanyi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20information%20helps%20Bayer%20establish%20%26quot%3Bone%20source%20of%20truth%2C%26quot%3B%20Ivanyi%20said%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20visibility%20of%20raw%20materials%20such%20as%20seeds%20and%20soybeans%20that%20need%20to%20be%20delivered%20at%20the%20right%20time%20to%20ensure%20a%20successful%20harvest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a705c9f6-570a-48ed-962f-3b9a2a4ea51f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20AI-powered%20tracking%20systems%20can%20boost%20customer%20satisfaction%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFourKites%20taps%20into%20Bayer's%20transportation-management%20system%2C%20data%20that%20shows%20which%20goods%20are%20assigned%20to%20various%20carriers%20along%20the%20supply%20chain.%20By%20using%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-machine-learning%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emachine-learning%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsc%2Fhow-artificial-intelligence-is-changing-everyday-technology-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eartificial-intelligence%20algorithms%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Bayer%20has%20seen%20an%20improvement%20in%20prediction%20quality%20of%20about%2048%25%20throughout%20an%20ocean%20journey%2C%20FourKites%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20recently%2C%20FourKites%20has%20also%20used%20generative%20AI%20to%20allow%20customers%20such%20as%20Bayer%20to%20ask%20AI%20chatbots%20questions%20about%20their%20logistics%20and%20what%20disruptions%20like%20the%20Baltimore%20bridge%20collapse%20may%20mean%20for%20them.%20The%20bots%20can%20even%20make%20recommendations%20on%20how%20to%20respond.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPriya%20Rajagopalan%2C%20the%20president%20of%20product%2C%20technology%2C%20and%20operations%20at%20FourKites%2C%20said%20the%20company%20launched%20more%20than%20eight%20years%20ago%20to%20give%20shipping%20visibility%20to%20large%20shippers%2C%20similar%20to%20how%20customers%20can%20easily%20track%20their%20orders%20via%20Amazon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFourKites%20tracks%20more%20than%203%20million%20shipments%20daily%20across%20roads%2C%20rails%2C%20the%20ocean%2C%20and%20air%2C%20reaching%20over%20200%20countries%20and%20territories%20and%20giving%20companies%20like%20Walmart%2C%20Coca-Cola%2C%20and%20Kraft%20Heinz%20better%20visibility%20into%20when%20the%20goods%20they%20produce%20will%20be%20delivered%20to%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22417d810c-87c2-4b21-bf0d-5a8d5f5666ae%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMonitoring%20complex%20ocean%20shipments%20to%20avoid%20supply-chain%20disruptions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20supply-chain%20disruptions%20from%20the%20pandemic%20led%20to%20great%20interest%20from%20large%20food%20and%20beverage%20companies%20to%20more%20closely%20track%20shipments%2C%20especially%20those%20moving%20across%20the%20ocean%2C%20which%20hadn't%20previously%20been%20as%20big%20of%20a%20focus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20scale%20of%20the%20disruption%20was%20so%20large%20that%20just%20the%20fact%20that%20nobody%20is%20monitoring%20it%20and%20they%20have%20no%20tech%20around%20it%20became%20such%20a%20point%20of%20vulnerability%2C%26quot%3B%20Rajagopalan%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20almost%20every%20chief%20supply-chain%20officer%20received%20the%20mandate%20that%20we%20cannot%20have%20these%20sorts%20of%20blind%20spots%20and%20areas%20of%20vulnerability.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20FourKites%20focused%20on%20providing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flast-mile-delivery-shipping-explained%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereal-time%20visibility%20for%20shipments%20on%20trucks%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20highly%20fragmented%20system%20with%20over%203%20million%20trucks%20handled%20by%20over%20half%20a%20million%20carriers%20on%20US%20roads%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20seas%20have%20seen%20more%20high-profile%20disruptions%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20including%20a%20container%20ship%20getting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftime