20planning%20to%20account%20for%20the%20delayed%20deliveries%2C%20instead%20focusing%20on%20making%20products%20with%20the%20goods%20it%20has%20on%20hand%20from%20other%20vendors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20tracking%20system%20also%20allows%20Bayer%20sales%20representatives%20to%20know%20when%20the%20seeds%20will%20be%20delivered%20to%20the%20farmer%20in%20Illinois.%20Previously%2C%20that%20representative%20would%20need%20to%20talk%20to%20someone%20in%20customer%20service%2C%20who%20would%20then%20call%20logistics%20and%20then%20call%20the%20carrier%20to%20get%20intel%20on%20disruptions.%20Now%2C%20all%20that%20information%20is%20available%20virtually.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20day%2C%20you%20are%20feeding%20into%20this%20kind%20of%20intelligence%20that%20I%20think%20is%20getting%20better%20and%20better%2C%26quot%3B%20Ivanyi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-bayer-uses-ai-tracking-complex-overseas-shipments-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716394550000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66464a819fc063e829b1e5c7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-bayer-uses-ai-tracking-complex-overseas-shipments-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bayer%20implemented%20FourKites'%20AI-powered%20real-time%20tracking%20in%202021%20to%20keep%20tabs%20on%20time-sensitive%20domestic%20and%20global%20shipments.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(John%20Kell)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-bayer-uses-ai-tracking-complex-overseas-shipments-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Marvel%20Sets%20Vision%20Series%20for%202026%20With%20Paul%20Bettany%2C%20%E2%80%98Star%20Trek%3A%20Picard%E2%80%99%20EP%20Terry%20Matalas%20as%20Showrunner%20(EXCLUSIVE)%22%2C%22content%22%3A