ed%20as%20Russia%20built%20up%20its%20forces%20on%20the%20Russian%20side%20of%20the%20border%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thetimes.co.uk%2Farticle%2Fspetsnaz-came-via-the-marshes-and-trees-i-had-to-call-in-artillery-vdjn8sqwp%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Times%20of%20London%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3Ereferring%20to%20the%20US-provided%20MGM-140%20Army%20Tactical%20Missile%20Systems.%3Cspan%3E%20He%20told%20the%20outlet%20that%20having%20to%20wait%20for%20the%20enemy%20to%20cross%20into%20Ukrainian%20territory%20proved%20costly.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20(R)%20and%20the%20Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy%20(L)%20meet%20during%20Zelenskyy's%20visit%20to%20Washington%20on%20Dec%2012%2C%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664ddafe14fb5b23cc5efd83%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221366%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUS%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20(R)%20and%20the%20Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy%20(L)%20meet%20during%20Zelenskyy's%20visit%20to%20Washington%20on%20Dec%2012%2C%202023.%3Cp%3EPhoto%20by%20Ukrainian%20Presidency%2FHandout%2FAnadolu%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20has%20long%20feared%20that%20a%20change%20in%20its%20policy%20could%20be%20seen%20by%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20as%20an%20escalation.%20Washington%20has%20also%20held%20this%20attitude%20when%20considering%20whether%20to%20send%20high-profile%20weaponry%20to%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFormer%20Under%20Secretary%20of%20State%20for%20Political%20Affairs%20Victoria%20Nuland%20pushed%20back%20on%20this%20rationale%20during%20a%20Sunday%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabcnews.go.com%2FPolitics%2Fweek-transcript-5-19-24-sen-chris-van%2Fstory%3Fid%3D110365911%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_