0will%20talk%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2248e0aa2d-fa67-488c-b90f-a770e00f6134%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20space%20with%20warm%20and%20cool%20light%20temperatures%20will%20look%20busy%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20designer%20hates%20to%20see%20warm-%20and%20cool-toned%20light%20bulbs%20within%20a%20single%20space.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20important%20to%20make%20sure%20the%20color%20temperature%20of%20the%20light%20bulbs%20or%20architectural%20lights%20are%20all%20the%20same%20within%20the%20space%2C%26quot%3B%20Moreira%20said.%20%26quot%3BOtherwise%2C%20it%20will%20look%20like%20the%20lights%20were%20an%20afterthought%20and%20look%20very%20busy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22af2bbcbd-2b9d-423c-b802-1f20755a851b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EBuying%20the%20wrong-sized%20furniture%20for%20a%20space%20can%20make%20it%20feel%20too%20empty%20or%20crowded%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20scale%20of%20your%20furniture%20is%20so%20important.%20When%20shopping%2C%20she%20said%2C%20consider%20the%20floor%20space%20you're%20working%20with%20as%20well%20as%20the%20architecture%20of%20the%20room.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BYou%20should%20have%20good%20traffic%20flow%20within%20the%20space%2C%20but%20it%20should%20never%20feel%20like%20it's%20missing%20a%20piece%20or%20feel%20empty%2C%26quot%3B%20Moreira%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fdd1b411-a8e2-46e0-8008-f730fb8783fa%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3ETry%20to%20avoid%20completely%20matching%20metal%20finishes%20within%20a%20space%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BMany%20people%20are%20very%20afraid%20of%20mixing%20metals%20and%20prefer%20all%20of%20the%20finishes%20to%20match%20exactly%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20always%20encourage%20my%20clients%20to%20mix%20metals.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%