%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20brief%20flash%20crash%20caused%20by%20the%20mistaken%20trade%20briefly%20wiped%20out%20%24322%20billion%20in%20market%20value.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20trading%20mistake%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fc-stock%3FmiRedirects%3D1%5C%22%3ECitigroup%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20resulted%20in%20a%20%2478%20million%20fine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20trader%20in%20Citigroup's%20London%20unit%20entered%20one%20too%20many%20zeros%20in%20a%20trade%20in%20May%202022%2C%20sparking%20a%20short-lived%20flash%20crash%20in%20European%20stocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20trade%20itself%20was%20entered%20during%20early%20European%20market%20hours%20and%20caused%20a%20five-minute%20flash%20crash%20in%20the%20OMX%20Stockholm%2030%20Index%2C%20wiping%20out%20as%20much%20as%20%24322%20billion%20at%20one%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Bloomberg%2C%20the%20trade%20was%20meant%20to%20hedge%20the%20bank's%20exposure%20to%20the%20MSCI%20World%20Index%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-05-22%2Fthe-15-minutes-on-a-citi-trading-desk-that-sparked-a-flash-crash%3Fsrnd%3Dhomepage-canada%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20trader%20meant%20to%20execute%20a%20trade%20that%20would%20create%20a%20basket%20of%20stocks%20valued%20at%20%2458%20million%2C%20they%20accidentally%20entered%2058%20million%20into%20the%20quantity%20field%2C%20ultimately%20creating%20a%20massive%20trade%20worth%20%24444%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECiti's%20trading%20systems%20fired%20off%20warnings%20and%20prevented%20much%20of%20the%20trade%20from%20going%20through%2C%20but%20not%20all%2C%20with%20about%20%241.4%20billion%20worth%20of%20the%20trade%20being%20executed%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20cascade%20of%20sales%20of%20European%20stocks%20across%20various%20European%20exchanges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUK%20regulators%20investigating%20the%20trading%20blunder%20leveled%20a%20%2478%20million%20penalty%20against%20Citigroup%20for%20the%20mistake%20on%20Wednesday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20immediate%20cause%20of%20the%20trading%20error%20was%20a%20manual%20input%20error%20by%20the%20trader.%20The%20error%20was%20then%20not%20identified%20by%20either%20of%20the%20firm's%20risk%20functions%20dedicated%20to%20real-time%20monitoring%20of%20the%20firm's%20trades%2C%20but%20by%20the%20trader%20some%2015%20minutes%20after%20the%20trade%20was%20entered%20into%20the%20firm's%20systems%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Bank%20of%20England's%20Prudential%20Regulatory%20Authority%20said%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%2478%20million%20fine%20from%20UK%20regulators%20is%20in%20addition%20to%20about%20%2450%20million%20Citigroup%20lost%20on%20the%20trade%2C%20bringing%20the%20total%20cost%20of%20the%20fat-finger%20trade%20to%20about%20%24130%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fciti-trader-fat-finger-flash-crash-trade-78-million-fine-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716392497000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664df42414fb5b23cc5f01aa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fciti-trader-fat-finger-flash-crash-trade-78-million-fine-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20trader%20accidentally%20entered%2058%20million%20into%20the%20quantity%20field%2C%20ultimately%20creating%20a%20massive%20trade%20that%20was%20worth%20%24444%20billion.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mfox%40businessinsider.com%20(Matthew%20Fox)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fciti-trader-fat-finger-flash-crash-trade-78-million-fine-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Constantin%20Film%20Appoints%20Viola%20J%C3%A4ger%20and%20Jan%20Ehlert%20as%20