In%20his%20first%20direct%20reaction%20to%20the%20alleged%20assault%20on%20his%20party's%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Swati%20Maliwal%2C%20which%20has%20kicked%20up%20a%20political%20firestorm%2C%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20has%20said%20he%20expects%20that%20a%20fair%20investigation%20will%20be%20conducted%20and%20justice%20will%20be%20done.%20The%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20chief%20stressed%2C%20however%2C%20that%20there%20are%20two%20versions%20of%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Maliwal%20has%20alleged%20that%20she%20was%20assaulted%20by%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20personal%20assistant%2C%20Bibhav%20Kumar%2C%20at%20the%20chief%20minister's%20residence%20on%20May%2013.%20The%20AAP%20leader%20claimed%20Mr%20Kumar%20had%20kicked%20her%20in%20the%20chest%2C%20stomach%20and%20pelvic%20area%20and%20had%20brutally%20%26quot%3Bdragged%20her%20and%20pulled%20her%20shirt%20up%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumar%20has%20been%20arrested%20and%20was%20sent%20to%20the%20custody%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20till%20Thursday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20news%20agency%20PTI%2C%20the%20AAP%20chief%20said%20the%20alleged%20assault%20is%20%26quot%3Bsub-judice%26quot%3B%20and%20him%20commenting%20on%20it%20could%20affect%20the%20proceedings.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20expect%20there%20will%20be%20a%20fair%20investigation.%20Justice%20should%20be%20served.%20There%20are%20two%20versions%20of%20the%20event.%20Police%20should%20investigate%20both%20versions%20fairly%20and%20justice%20should%20be%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHitting%20back%20strongly%20at%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20Ms%20Maliwal%20said%20it%20was%20ironic%20that%20the%20person%20who%20had%20%26quot%3Bassassinated%20her%20character%26quot%3B%20and%20called%20her%20a%20%26quot%3BBJP%20agent%26quot%3B%20was%20now%20calling%20for%20a%20free%20and%20fair%20investigation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20unleashing%20the%20entire%20army%20of%20lea