Arvind%20Kejriwal%20has%20said%20if%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20comes%20to%20power%20in%20the%20ongoing%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20it%20would%20%26quot%3Bfree%26quot%3B%20the%20judiciary%20from%20the%20%26quot%3Btremendous%20pressure%26quot%3B%20it%20is%20facing.%20This%2C%20he%20added%2C%20will%20lead%20to%20his%20release%20from%20jail%20on%20June%205%2C%20as%20all%20cases%20against%20him%20are%20%26quot%3Bbogus%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20--%20arrested%20in%20the%20Delhi%20liquor%20policy%20case%20and%20freed%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20granted%20him%20interim%20bail%20earlier%20this%20month%20--%20had%20earlier%20said%20if%20the%20Opposition%20wins%20he%20would%20be%20free%20the%20day%20after%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20statement%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20told%20PTI%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20judiciary%20is%20under%20tremendous%20pressure%20currently.%20Everyone%20knows%20how%20much%20pressure%20they%20are%20working%20under%20now%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20will%20put%20pressure%20on%20courts%20to%20have%20him%20freed%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20not%20put%20any%20pressure.%20But%20if%20the%20pressure%20is%20lifted%20from%20the%20judiciary%20then%20justice%20will%20start%20to%20be%20served%20fairly%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20the%20cases%20against%20me%20are%20bogus.%20There%20is%20no%20money%20trail%20anywhere.%20Not%20a%20single%20paisa%20has%20been%20traced.%20If%20there%20was%20corruption%2C%20where%20has%20the%20money%20gone%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20on%20March%2021%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20Delhi%20liquor%20policy%20case.%20On%20May%2010%2C%20he%20was%20released%20from%20Tihar%20Jail%20so%20he%20could%20join%20his%20party's%20campaign%20for%20the%20ongoing%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%2