ngladesh-mp-anwarul-azim-anar-murdered-blood-stains-found-in-flat-kolkata-cops-5721556%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmissing-bangladesh-mp-anwarul-azim-anar-murdered-blood-stains-found-in-flat-kolkata-cops-5721556%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Farmer%E2%80%99s%20Startup%20Takes%20Vets%20to%20Doorsteps%20In%20Rural%20India%2C%20Earn%20Rs%208%20Crore%2FYear%20Saving%20Cattle%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20year%20was%202019.%20It%20was%20a%20pitch-dark%20night.%20Jaipur-based%20Manish%20Prahlad%20had%20retired%20to%20the%20bed%20after%20tending%20to%20his%20livestock.%20The%20next%20morning%20when%20he%20woke%20up%2C%20he%20found%20all%20of%20his%20nine%20buffaloes%20lying%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20breathing%20their%20last.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20could%20not%20understand%20what%20caused%20the%20sudden%20discomfort%20in%20my%20buffaloes.%20They%20were%20short%20on%20breath.%20I%20saw%20them%20dying%20one%20by%20one%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20went%20to%20the%20local%20veterinarian%20to%20understand%20the%20cause%20of%20sudden%20deaths%20of%20my%20cattle%20but%20he%20had%20no%20convincing%20answer.%20He%20told%20me%20there%20were%20many%20farmers%20whose%20cattle%20were%20dying%20similarly.%20But%20the%20reason%20was%20unknown%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeartbroken%20Manish%20went%20haywire%20as%20these%20buffaloes%20were%20his%20only%20assets.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20%3Cem%3Enana%20%3C%2Fem%3E(maternal%20grandfather)%20gave%20a%20%3Cem%3EMurrah%3C%2Fem%3E%20buffalo%20to%20my%20parents%20as%20a%20wedding%20gift.%20Murrah%20is%20considered%20to%20be%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20best%20dairy%20type%20buffalo%20and%20is%20one%20of%20the%20prestigious%20breeds%2C%20also%20known%20as%20%E2%80%98Black%20Gold%E2%80%99%20for%20farmers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20buffalo%20was%20for%20our%20breed%20line%20and%20was%20not%20for%20commercial%20purposes.%20Usually%2C%20%3Cem%3EMurrah%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebuffaloes%20have%20a%20market%20value%20of%20Rs%203%20lakh%2C%20and%20its%20pure%20breeders%20are%20sold%20for%20a%20whopping%20Rs%2035%20to%2040%20lakh.%20They%20were%20our%20treasures.%20We%20could%20not%20claim%20insurance%20amounts%20as%20the%20cause%20of%20death%20was%20not%20known.%20This%20news%20broke%20me%20completely%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20laments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FManish-Prahlad-1716381129.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22With%20536.76%20million%2C%20India%20has%20the%20largest%20livestock%20population%20in%20the%20world.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FManish-Prahlad-1716381129.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FManish-Prahlad-1716381129-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FManish-Prahlad-1716381129-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FManish-Prahlad-1716381129-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FManish-Prahlad-1716381129-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350777%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWith%20536.76%20million%2C%20India%20has%20the%20largest%20livestock%20population%20in%20the%20world.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManish%20was%20very%20close%20to%20his%20buffaloes%20as%20it%20was%20through%20them%20that%20his%20mother%20was%20able%20to%20pay%20his%20school%20fees.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20mother%20was%20so%20upset.%20The%20health%20of%20livestock%20is%20extremely%20important%20for%20the%20income%20generation%20of%20farmers%20like%20us.%20So%2C%20it%20is%20not%20farmers%20who%20rear%20animals%2C%20it%20is%20these%20animals%20who%20take%20care%20of%20the%20farmers.%20I%20realised%20if%20I%20faced%20this%20issue%20living%20in%20Jaipur%20then%20there%20would%20be%20so%20many%20small%20farmers%20going%20through%20the%20same%20agony%20in%20remote%20areas%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20day%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20work%20on%20improving%20medical%20facilities%20for%20livestock%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20536.76%20million%2C%20India%20has%20the%20largest%20livestock%20population%20in%20the%20world.%20Livestock%20plays%20a%20key%20role%20and%20the%20sector%20contributes%20about%206.20%20percent%20of%20the%20total%20GDP%2C%20and%20yet%2C%20Manish%20says%2C%20livestock%20healthcare%20remains%20ignored.%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20has%20less%20than%2012%2C500%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F199843%2Fandhra-vet-risks-life-to-save-300-wild-animals-shows-true-humanity%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eveterinary%20clinics%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20owing%20to%20the%20system%E2%80%99s%20apathy%2C%20farmers%20continue%20losing%20their%20only%20assets%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20address%20this%2C%20he%20launched%20%E2%80%98Verdant%20Impact%E2%80%99%20in%202020%20to%20offer%20holistic%20services%20%E2%80%94%20including%20telemedicine%20facilities%2C%20animal%20ICU%2C%20remote%20monitoring%2C%20cattle%20commerce%2C%20and%20virtual%20veterinary%20consultations%20for%20livestock%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOne-stop%20solution%20for%20cattle%20care%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOriginally%20from%20Banswara%2C%20Manish%20dropped%20out%20of%20his%20first%20year%20of%20PhD%20to%20focus%20on%20livestock%20healthcare.%20Talking%20about%20the%20issues%20in%20the%20field%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CUnlike%20cats%20and%20dogs%2C%20the%20biggest%20issue%20is%20that%20farmers%20cannot%20carry%20them%20to%20hospitals%20as%20transportation%20costs%20are%20high%20and%20the%20process%20is%20inconvenient.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FManish-Prahlad-1-1716381157.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Livestock%20plays%20a%20key%20role%20and%20the%20sector%20contributes%20about%206.20%20percent%20of%20the%20total%20GDP%2C%20and%20yet%20their%20healthcare%20remains%20ignored.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FManish-Prahlad-1-1716381157.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FManish-Prahlad-1-1716381157-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FManish-Prahlad-1-1716381157-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FManish-Prahlad-1-1716381157-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FManish-Prahlad-1-1716381157-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350778%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ELivestock%20plays%20a%20key%20role%20and%20the%20sector%20contributes%20about%206.20%20percent%20of%20the%20total%20GDP%2C%20and%20yet%20their%20healthcare%20remains%20ignored.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTelemedicine%20allows%20farmers%20to%20connect%20to%20doctors%20anytime%20and%20anywhere.%20The%20purpose%20is%20to%20give%20doorstep%20facility%2C%20as%20a%20doctor%20visit%20costs%20up%20to%20Rs%20500%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20common%20concerns%20in%20livestock%20are%20diseases%20like%20foot%20and%20mouth%2C%20fever%2C%20digestive%20problems%20in%20monsoon%2C%20lumpy%20skin%2C%20and%20poor%20nutrition%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20find%20a%20convenient%20solution%20to%20address%20the%20diseases%2C%20Manish%20introduced%20a%20mobile%20application%20wherein%20farmers%20upload%20photos%2C%20videos%2C%20and%20detailed%20descriptions%20of%20their%20animals%20for%20consultation%20from%20a%20veterinarian%2C%20who%20later%20on%20shares%20prescriptions%20and%20remedies.%20If%20necessary%2C%20farmers%20are%20connected%20with%20nearby%20veterinarians%20for%20field%20visits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20that%20case%2C%20we%20provide%20an%20SOS%20button%20in%20our%20app%20wherein%20farmers%20can%20book%20consultations%20from%20nearby%20doctors%2C%20similar%20to%20Uber%20and%20Ola%20where%20nearby%20taxis%20are%20displayed%20to%20get%20quick%20responses.%20Our%20doctors%20serve%20till%20a%20range%20of%2040%20km%20and%20our%20response%20time%20is%20within%20an%20hour%2C%20which%20is%20very%20efficient%20considering%20rural%20terrain%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FManish-Prahlad-2-1716381214.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Telemedicine%20allows%20farmers%20to%20connect%20to%20doctors%20anytime%20and%20anywhere.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FManish-Prahlad-2-1716381214.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FManish-Prahlad-2-1716381214-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FManish-Prahlad-2-1716381214-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FManish-Prahlad-2-1716381214-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FManish-Prahlad-2-1716381214-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350779%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETelemedicine%20allows%20farmers%20to%20connect%20to%20doctors%20anytime%20and%20anywhere.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20Manish%20has%20set%20up%20more%20than%2010%2C000%20telemedicine%20centres%20and%20onboarded%20over%201%2C700%20veterinarians%20and%20para%20veterinarians%20in%2016%20states%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Punjab%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20Bihar%2C%20Telangana%2C%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Assam%2C%20Meghalaya%2C%20Manipur%2C%20Mizoram%2C%20Nagaland%2C%20Tripura%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20and%20Haryana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20conducts%20over%202%2C500%20telemedical%20consultancy%20calls%20per%20day%20and%20charges%20Rs%2090%20for%20a%20consultation%20with%20the%20expert%20whereas%20Rs%20150%20for%20a%20field%20visit%2C%20which%20Manish%20says%20is%20more%20than%20double%20the%20market%20which%20charges%20Rs%20300-500.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20this%2C%20he%20has%20also%20designed%20Radio%20Frequency%20Identification%20(RFID)%20tags%20to%20monitor%20and%20trace%20the%20health%2C%20location%2C%20and%20movement%20of%20livestock.%20It%20also%20stores%20prescriptions%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F260896%2Fodisha-balaram-sahu-free-doctor-treatment-cow-cattle-diseases-inspiring%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edisease%20history%20%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20the%20cattle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20now%2C%20Verdant%20Impact%20is%20associated%20with%20more%20than%20six%20lakh%20farmers.%20Of%20this%2C%20more%20than%201.7%20lakh%20are%20directly%20benefitting%20through%20teleconsultations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20impact%20of%20his%20work%2C%20Manish%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CAmong%20the%20major%20health%20issues%20in%20livestock%20were%20productivity%20and%20difficulties%20in%20pregnancies%20owing%20to%20malnutrition.%20We%20provide%20herbal%20treatment%20that%20boosts%20suitable%20ovulation%20period%20in%20cattle.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FManish-Prahlad-3-1716381268.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Verdant%20Impact%20is%20associated%20with%20more%20than%20six%20lakh%20farmers.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FManish-Prahlad-3-1716381268.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FManish-Prahlad-3-1716381268-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FManish-Prahlad-3-1716381268-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FManish-Prahlad-3-1716381268-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FManish-Prahlad-3-1716381268-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350780%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EVerdant%20Impact%20is%20associated%20with%20more%20than%20six%20lakh%20farmers.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20bovines%20usually%20conceive%20in%2037%20to%2040%20months%20if%20it%20is%20malnourished%20but%20when%20you%20provide%20good%20nutrition%2C%20they%20are%20ready%20to%20conceive%20in%2022%20to%2027%20months.%20This%20gives%20farmers%20an%20extra%20cycle%20for%20gestation%20before%20the%20bovine%20is%20ready%20for%20the%20next%20calving.%20Depending%20on%20the%20breed%2C%20they%20earn%20an%20extra%20income%20of%20up%20to%20Rs%202%20to%203%20la