re%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20tryst%20with%20organic%20farming%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOrganic%20farming%20is%20not%20easy%20%E2%80%94%20this%20is%20what%20Ganesh%20realised%20when%20he%20began%20to%20delve%20deeper%20into%20the%20subject%20around%202002.%20But%20even%20so%2C%20as%20he%20weighed%20the%20long-term%20fruits%20(pun%20intended)%20of%20organic%20techniques%20with%20the%20allures%20of%20chemical%20farming%2C%20he%20knew%20the%20former%20held%20more%20promise.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%201978%20my%20father%20had%20planted%201%2C000%20mango%20saplings%20on%20the%20land.%20He%20did%20this%20at%20a%20time%20when%20Ratnagiri%20was%20experiencing%20a%20harsh%20climate%2C%20less%20rainfall%2C%20undeveloped%20roads%20and%20power%20cuts%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20recalls%20watching%20his%20father%20climbing%20to%20heights%20sometimes%2C%20to%20water%20the%20trees%20when%20the%20rain%20gods%20weren%E2%80%99t%20being%20kind.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20he%20persisted%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ganesh%2C%20adding%20that%20the%201%2C000%20trees%20flourished.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20joined%20my%20father%20in%20farming%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F347565%2Fgrow-mangoes-chikoo-fruits-on-trees-urban-gardener-jayanti-sahoo-terrace-gardening-tips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplant%20another%201%2C000%20mango%20saplings%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20today%2C%20we%20have%20over%202%2C000%20mango%20trees.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaturally%2C%20the%20farm%20always%20had%20an%20audience.%20People%20were%20intrigued%20at%20how%20the%20father-son%20duo%20had%20created%20a%20yellow%20oasis%2C%20and%20the%20organic%20methods%20they%20had%20used%20to%20achieve%20the%20feat.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20many%20guests%20who%20wanted%20to%20observe%20how%20we%20were%20preparing%20our%20organic%20fertilisers%20from%20cow%20dung%20(we%20had%2035%20cows%20in%20our%20shed)%2C%20how%20we%20used%20neem%20to%20make%20our%20pesticides%2C%20and%20how%20our%20mangoes%20were%20thriving%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ganesh%20points%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmango-homestay-5-1715946632.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Ganesh%20Agro%20Tourism%20homestay%20lies%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20Ratnagiri%20and%20Sindhudurg%20districts%20of%20Maharashtra%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmango-homestay-5-1715946632.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmango-homestay-5-1715946632-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmango-homestay-5-1715946632-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmango-homestay-5-1715946632-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmango-homestay-5-1715946632-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350407%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Ganesh%20Agro%20Tourism%20homestay%20lies%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20Ratnagiri%20and%20Sindhudurg%20districts%20of%20Maharashtra%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Ganesh%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmango-homestay-4-1715946692.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20homestay%20has%20authentic%20rooms%20with%20one%20even%20being%20a%20mud%20room%20without%20air%20conditioning%2C%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmango-homestay-4-1715946692.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmango-homestay-4-1715946692-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmango-homestay-4-1715946692-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmango-homestay-4-1715946692-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmango-homestay-4-1715946692-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350408%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20homestay%20has%20authentic%20rooms%20with%20one%20even%20being%20a%20mud%20room%20without%20air%20conditioning%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Ganesh%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20farm%20getting%20so%20much%20attention%2C%20Ganesh%20began%20thinking%20along%20the%20lines%20of%20creating%20a%20model%20which%20would%20combine%20tourism%20with%20agriculture%20but%20he%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20quite%20put%20his%20finger%20on%20what%20this%20would%20be%3B%20until%20in%202008%2C%20an%20experience%20changed%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20may%20have%20heard%20of%20food%20scientist-turned-farmer%20Chandrasekhar%20Bhadsavle%20%E2%80%94%20famous%20for%20introducing%20the%20Saguna%20Rice%20Technique%20(SRT)%20among%20a%20handful%20of%20farmers%20in%20Neral%20(Karjat)%20in%202013%20and%20for%20championing%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20agro-tourism%20initiative%20%E2%80%98Saguna%20Baug%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20is%20located%2075%20km%20from%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20degraded%20land%2C%20the%20Baug%20was%20transformed%20into%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F252647%2Fmango-farm-ultra-high-density-planting-uhdp-kesar-alphonso-profits-farmer-success-story%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethriving%20land%20with%20food%20crops%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20bamboo%2C%20livestock%20and%20fish%3B%20a%20space%20that%20promoted%20the%20surrounding%20wild%20biodiversity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20day%20while%20on%20a%20drive%2C%20Ganesh%20came%20across%20Saguna%20Baug%20and%20having%20heard%20so%20much%20about%20the%20place%2C%20decided%20to%20stop%20by.%20They%20say%20some%20things%20can%20change%20your%20life%E2%80%99s%20trajectory%20completely.%20For%20Ganesh%2C%20a%20guided%20tour%20through%20the%20green%20space%20with%20Bhadsavle%E2%80%99s%20running%20commentary%20on%20how%20freeing%20nature%20could%20really%20be%20was%20one%20such%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20was%20all%20I%20needed%20to%20confirm%20my%20faith%20in%20an%20idea%20that%20I%20had%20had%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ganesh%2C%20adding%20that%20his%20vision%20finally%20got%20a%20name.%20He%20decided%20to%20build%20an%20agro-tourism%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhere%20mangoes%20play%20host%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minute%20you%20step%20into%20Ganesh%20Agro%20Tourism%20homestay%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20be%20able%20to%20tell%20the%20stark%20difference%20between%20the%20city%20air%20from%20the%20fresh%20gusts%20here.%20Mango%20trees%20move%20almost%20melodically%2C%20the%20branches%20causing%20a%20rustle%20that%20makes%20you%20stop%20and%20want%20to%20interpret.%20Watching%20these%20beauties%20and%20feasting%20on%20their%20fruits%20constitutes%20a%20great%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGanesh%20lets%20us%20in%20on%20the%20inception%20behind%20this%20homestay%20idea%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20once%20my%20father%E2%80%99s%20packing%20unit.%20When%20we%20started%20getting%20so%20many%20guests%20visiting%20us%20to%20watch%20our%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332094%2Frajasthan-rubi-pareek-doubles-profit-with-organic-farming-gives-free-training%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eorganic%20farming%3C%2Fa%3E%20practices%2C%20we%20thought%20it%20would%20be%20nice%20to%20create%20a%20place%20where%20they%20could%20stay.%20And%20so%20we%20decided%20to%20modify%20the%20packing%20unit%20into%20a%20homestay.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmango-homestay-3-1715947573.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20homestay%20is%20built%20in%20typical%20Maharashtrian%20style%20and%20is%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20paddy%20and%20mango%20plantations%2C%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmango-homestay-3-1715947573.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmango-homestay-3-1715947573-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmango-homestay-3-1715947573-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmango-homestay-3-1715947573-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmango-homestay-3-1715947573-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350410%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20homestay%20is%20built%20in%20typical%20Maharashtrian%20style%20and%20is%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20paddy%20and%20mango%20plantations%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Ganesh%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmango-homestay-2-1715947684.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22At%20the%20homestay%2C%20guests%20are%20treated%20