tly%2C%20Ganesh%E2%80%99s%20mangoes%20make%20their%20way%20to%20markets%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20Thane%2C%20Kolhapur%2C%20Sangli%2C%20Nashik%2C%20and%20Pune.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%20that%20while%20they%20did%20try%20their%20hands%20out%20at%20other%20vegetables%2C%20growing%20mangoes%20seemed%20the%20most%20lucrative%20option.%20%E2%80%9CAside%20from%20the%20demand%20for%20mangoes%2C%20there%20are%20other%20factors%20that%20make%20them%20suitable%20for%20us%20to%20grow.%20When%20we%20tried%20growing%20vegetables%2C%20cows%20would%20eat%20them%2C%20and%20we%20did%20not%20have%20money%20to%20hire%20people%20who%20would%20keep%20a%20watch%20on%20the%20fields.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%20the%20family%20decided%20to%20channel%20their%20energies%20into%20mangoes.%20And%20it%20is%20a%20bonus%20that%20Ratnagiri%E2%80%99s%20prowess%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F347512%2Forder-mangoes-ratnagiri-devgadh-alphonso-jardalu-online-in-mumbai-bengaluru-delhi-pune%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAlphonso%20mangoes%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20GI-tag%20proof.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reason%20for%20Ratnagiri%20being%20hailed%20as%20the%20best%20for%20Alphonso%20mangoes%2C%20Ganesh%20says%2C%20is%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20laterite%20soil%20here.%20%E2%80%9CAdd%20to%20this%20the%20favourable%20climate!%E2%80%9D%20He%20emphasises%20that%20the%20mangoes%20he%20sells%20are%20genuine%20and%20have%20a%20unique%20identity.%20The%20Alphonso%20mango%20has%20long%20since%20worn%20the%20crown%20for%20being%20one%20of%20the%20sweetest%2C%20most%20aromatic%20varieties%2C%20named%20after%20Portuguese%20general%20and%20military%20specialist%20Afonso%20de%20Albuquerque%2C%20who%20assisted%20in%20establishing%20Portuguese%20colonies%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20notes%20of%20citrus%20and%20honey%2C%20the%20Ratnagiri%20Alphonso%20prides%20itself%20on%20a%20delicious%20pulp%20that%20is%20hugged%20by%20thin%2C%20firm%20skin%20with%20a%20longer%20shelf-life%20than%20their%20counterparts.%20And%20Ganesh%20is%20thrilled%20to%20be%20cultivating%20this%20work%20of%20art.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20anyone%20who%20wonders%20what%20Ganesh%20busies%20himself%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20year%20%E2%80%94%20aside%20from%20summers%20%E2%80%94%20he%20cautions%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F347996%2Frare-mangoes-available-in-india-alphonso-sindhri-mango-expensive-mangoes-summer-season%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emango%20season%3C%2Fa%3E%20lasts%20for%20two%20months.%20But%20the%20other%2010%20months%20go%20into%20the%20maintenance%20of%20the%20land%2C%20cleaning%20the%20gardens%2C%20spraying%20the%20trees%2C%20putting%20fertiliser%2C%20and%20watching%20the%20fruits%20start%20to%20flourish.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20summer%20season%20is%20when%20the%20family%20reaps%20the%20rewards%20of%20this%20hard%20work.%20Sharing%20how%20a%20love%20for%20nature%20has%20always%20coloured%20his%20choices%2C%20Ganesh%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20ventured%20into%20farming%20just%20out%20of%20passion.%20And%20it%20was%20the%20best%20decision.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETo%20book%20your%20stay%20and%20experience%20an%20authentic%20farm%20life%2C%20you%20can%20reach%20out%20to%20Ganesh%20at%209422433676%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716275096000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmango-homestay-7-1715946426.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D350402%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ganesh%20Ashok%20Ranade%20transitioned%20from%20being%20a%20commerce%20graduate%20to%20a%20dedicated%20organic%20farmer%2C%20creating%20a%2040-acre%20agro-tourism%20haven%20in%20Ratnagiri.%20The%20homestay%20offers%20guests%20a%20hands-