0starry-eyed%20child%20who%20dreamt%20of%20doing%20something%20great.%20%E2%80%9CGiven%20the%20times%20that%20I%20was%20born%20in%2C%20my%20family%20was%20very%20supportive%20and%20liberal.%20I%20scored%20good%20marks%20on%20the%20school%20board%20exams%20and%20got%20admitted%20to%20medical%20school%20in%20Ajmer%20and%20Delhi%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20grew%20up%20in%20luxury%2C%20which%20allowed%20her%20the%20freedom%20to%20choose%20her%20own%20path%20in%20life.%20So%20she%20decided%20to%20pursue%20a%20career%20in%20medical%20science.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20did%20my%20internship%20in%20Ajmer%2C%20where%20I%20met%20my%20husband.%20We%20decided%20to%20get%20married%20and%20moved%20to%20Jaipur%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201968%2C%20Dr%20Maya%20gave%20birth%20to%20her%20son.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20that%2C%20I%20chose%20to%20pursue%20a%20diploma%20in%20anesthesiology%20because%20it%20was%20a%20career%20that%20I%20could%20manage%20while%20raising%20a%20family.%20By%20the%20time%20I%20completed%20my%20diploma%2C%20I%20had%20also%20given%20birth%20to%20another%20child%2C%20my%20daughter%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201972%2C%20she%20also%20did%20an%20MS%20in%20anaesthesia.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20also%20giving%20lectures%20on%20anaesthesia%20at%20a%20medical%20college%20in%20Jaipur%20where%20I%20came%20across%20an%20opportunity.%20It%20was%20a%20fellowship%20in%20London%20for%20paediatric%20anaesthesia.%20With%20my%20family%E2%80%99s%20support%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20attend%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-6-1715867697.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-6-1715867697.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-6-1715867697-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-6-1715867697-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-6-1715867697-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-6-1715867697-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350314%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr%20Maya%20Tandon%2C%20a%20Padma%20Shri%20Awardee.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20her%20fellowship%2C%20she%20returned%20to%20India%20and%20began%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F251637%2Frajasthan-startup-newndra-innovation-ganesh-ram-jangir-jaipur-belt-back-pain-farmer-help-make-in-india-ros174%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworking%20in%20Jaipur.%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fa%3EThe%20role%20of%20an%20anesthesiologist%20is%20often%20seen%20as%20a%20behind-the-curtain%20job.%20However%2C%20for%20me%20and%20in%20medical%20sciences%2C%20the%20patient%E2%80%99s%20life%20depends%20on%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20emphasises%2C%20highlighting%20her%20deep%20interest%20in%20lifesaving%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201975%2C%20she%20earned%20the%20honour%20of%20becoming%20superintendent%20and%20spent%20the%20rest%20of%20her%20career%20managing%20the%20hospital%20while%20serving%20as%20the%20head%20of%20anaesthesia%20at%20Sawai%20Man%20Singh%20Hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20around%20the%20time%20of%20my%20retirement%20in%201985%20when%20the%20Rajasthan%20Police%20Academy%20in%20Jaipur%20contacted%20me%20and%20requested%20I%20give%20a%20three-day%20course%20on%20road%20safety%20and%20lifesaving.%20I%20readily%20agreed%20to%20the%20request%2C%20unaware%20that%20it%20would%20shape%20the%20course%20of%20my%20post-retirement%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Maya%20reminisces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20course%20was%20very%20successful%20and%20all%20the%20senior%20officers%20posted%20on%20highways%20in%20and%20around%20Jaipur%20were%20sent%20to%20her%20for%20yet%20another%20course.%20%E2%80%9CA%20photographer%20had%20come%20to%20take%20some%20pictures%20of%20the%20event.%20It%20was%20a%20few%20months%20later%20that%20he%20rang%20me%20up%20and%20told%20me%20that%20I%20had%20saved%20his%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20photographer%20had%20been%20in%20an%20accident%20and%20could%20feel%20bleeding%20in%20his%20inner%20thighs%20and%20back.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20people%20around%20him%20were%20not%20sure%20how%20to%20help%20him%20and%20were%20taking%20pictures%20of%20him.%20He%20explained%20someone%20to%20lift%20him%20and%20put%20him%20in%20a%20certain%20position%20that%20slowed%20the%20bleeding%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20narrates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20timely%20move%20reduced%20the%20blood%20loss%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F317185%2Fbollywood-celebrity-photographer-munna-thaakur-recalls-struggle-story%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaved%20the%20photographer%E2%80%99s%20life.%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%9CHis%20words%20and%20appreciation%20made%20me%20realise%20the%20importance%20of%20offering%20such%20courses.%20It%20also%20revealed%20the%20sad%20reality%20of%20the%20state%20of%20road%20safety%20in%20India.%20Not%20one%20of%20the%20persons%20in%20the%20crowd%20knew%20lifesaving%20steps%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20an%20intention%20to%20change%20the%20scenario%20of%20road%20safety%20in%20India%2C%20Dr%20Maya%20started%20the%20Sahayta%20Trust.%20Since%20then%2C%20she%20has%20given%20free%20courses%2C%20seminars%2C%20and%20lectures%20to%20over%201%2C33%2C000%20individuals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20th