hool%20where%20her%20mother%20had%20to%20lie%20about%20her%20profession.%20Being%20upfront%20would%20result%20in%20no%20school%20admitting%20the%20child.%20As%20much%20as%20her%20mother%20tried%20to%20shield%20her%2C%20when%20the%20school%20and%20her%20classmates%20realised%20the%20truth%2C%20life%20became%20hell%20for%20young%20Sandhya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20started%20with%20bullying%20over%20my%20skin%20colour.%20They%20would%20call%20me%20different%20names%2C%20including%20a%20%E2%80%98black%20crow%E2%80%99%20and%20more%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%20It%20got%20so%20bad%20that%20her%20classmates%20once%20pushed%20her%20head%20into%20a%20commode%20as%20they%20told%20her%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%20belong%20here%2C%20stay%20here.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETeachers%20too%20ridiculed%20her%20and%20made%20her%20sit%20on%20a%20separate%20bench%20at%20the%20back.%20While%20this%20abuse%20continued%20in%20school%2C%20she%20was%20sexually%20abused%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20raped%20multiple%20times%20when%20I%20was%20between%2010%20and%2016%20years%20old.%20My%20abuser%20would%20warn%20me%20that%20if%20I%20told%20anyone%20about%20it%2C%20no%20one%20would%20believe%20me.%20Every%20time%20he%20abused%20me%2C%20he%20told%20me%20that%20I%20deserved%20this.%20I%20heard%20the%20same%20thing%20everywhere%20that%20I%20deserved%20all%20the%20abuse%20because%20of%20my%20background%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThings%20changed%20for%20her%20when%20she%20moved%20to%20Kerala%20in%20Class%2010%2C%20away%20from%20abuse%20and%20a%20city%20where%20no%20one%20knew%20what%20her%20mother%20did%20several%20years%20ago.%20However%2C%20the%20trauma%20of%20the%20first%2014%20years%20of%20her%20life%20led%20to%20many%20difficulties%20including%20her%20studies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20light%20in%20the%20tunnel%20appeared%20for%20her%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20newspaper%20cutting%20about%20Shweta%20Katti%2C%20who%20became%20the%20first%20girl%20fr