wn%20in%20Odisha%E2%80%99s%20warm%20climate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20love%20keeping%20rare%20plants%20inside%20my%20garden.%20Sometimes%20it%20is%20challenging%20as%20well%2C%20given%20the%20temperature%20here%20rises%20to%2046%20degrees%20in%20the%20summer.%20But%20this%20challenge%20is%20what%20exactly%20makes%20it%20fun%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20control%20the%20temperature%2C%20he%20has%20established%20a%20small%20greenhouse%20where%20he%20keeps%20new%20saplings%20for%202-3%20months%20to%20help%20them%20acclimatise.%20%E2%80%9CI%20introduce%20them%20to%20direct%20sunlight%20slowly%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20Miyazaki%20mango%20plant%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20planted%20it%20directly%20on%20the%20ground%20floor%20of%20my%20house.%20Its%20sapling%20cost%20me%20Rs%202%2C500%20and%20I%20did%20not%20want%20to%20take%20any%20risk.%20I%20let%20the%20sapling%20settle%20into%20the%20soil.%20After%20two%20months%2C%20I%20added%20cow%20dung%2C%20bone%20meal%2C%20neem%20and%20mustard%20cakes%20to%20the%20plant%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSubrat-Nath-3-1-1715319776.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22For%20Subrat%2C%20growing%20rare%20plants%20is%20just%20a%20hobby%20and%20these%20plants%20are%20his%20only%20treasures.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSubrat-Nath-3-1-1715319776.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSubrat-Nath-3-1-1715319776-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSubrat-Nath-3-1-1715319776-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSubrat-Nath-3-1-1715319776-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSubrat-Nath-3-1-1715319776-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-349615%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EFor%20Subrat%2C%20growing%20rare%20plants%20is%20just%20a%20hobby%20and%20these%20plants%20are%20his%20only%20treasures.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20like%20his%20parents%2C%20Subrat%20believes%20in%20giving%20traditional%20fertilisers%20to%20plants.%20%E2%80%9CAny%20fruiting%20plant%20requires%20nitrogen%20for%20leaves%20and%20stem%20growth%2C%20phosphorus%20for%20root%20development%2C%20and%20potash%20for%20flower%20and%20fruit%20growth.%20We%20get%20these%20nutrients%20in%20cow%20dung%20itself.%20I%20do%20not%20make%20any%20other%20fancy%20fertilisers.%20Cow%20dung%20is%20enough%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Subrat%20does%20not%20aim%20to%20sell%20the%20Miyazaki%20mangoes%2C%20he%20does%20sell%20saplings%20of%20the%20rare%201%2C000%20petal%20lotus%20and%20other%20water%20lily%20varieties.%20Last%20year%2C%20he%20earned%20an%20annual%20income%20of%20Rs%201%20lakh%20through%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20grow%20any%20rare%20plant%2C%20one%20must%20do%20a%20detailed%20study%20on%20the%20kind%20of%20temperature%20and%20humidity%20they%20require%20and%20the%20pot%20size.%20For%20instance%2C%20I%20grow%20the%201%2C000%20petal%20lotus%20in%20a%20bigger%20pot%20of%204%20ft%20width%20and%202%20ft%20of%20depth%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhereas%2C%20I%20use%20a%20pot%20of%20one%20ft%20width%20and%20seven%20inch%20depth%20for%20micro%20lotuses.%20We%20must%20also%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20lotuses%20and%20water%20lilies%20do%20not%20thrive%20in%20hard%20water%20and%20require%206%20to%207%20hours%20of%20sunlight%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubrat%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20not%20a%20pro.%20Growing%20rare%20plants%20is%20just%20my%20hobby%20and%20these%20plants%20are%20my%20only%20treasures.%20Also%2C%20I%20come%20across%20many%20people%20who%20make%20excuses%20that%20they%20cannot%20grow%20plants%20because%20of%20small%20spaces.%20With%20my%20example%2C%20I%20want%20to%20show%20that%20anyone%20can%20grow%20plants%2C%20even%20the%20rarest%20ones%20at%20home.%20My%20objective%20will%20be%20fulfilled%20when%20more%20and%20more%20people%20come%20forward%20to%20recreate%20my%20work.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%20All%20photos%3A%20Subrat%20Nath.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715855270000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSubrat-Nath-5-1715319960.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D349604%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Odisha%20resident%20Subrat%20Nath%20has%20turned%20his%20home%20into%20a%20mini%20garden%20with%20rare%20flowers%20and%20fruit%20plants.%20His%20exotic%20collection%20includes%20the%20Miyazaki%20mango%20which%20sells%20for%20Rs%202.5%20lakh%20per%20kg.%20With%20lilies%2C%20lotuses%2C%20and%20other%20rare%20plants%20thriving%20at%20home%2C%20Subrat%20hopes%20his%20work%20will%20inspire%20others%20to%20pick%20up%20gardening.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22REI%20Workers%20Say%20Union%20Effort%20Has%20Prompted%20A%20Disciplinary%20Crackdown%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22Employees%20believe%20the%20retailer%2C%20known%20for%20its%20progressive%20image%2C%20is%20using%20%26quot%3Bperformance%20improvement%20plans%26quot%3B%20to%20force%20them%20out.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715807818000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fimg.huffingtonpost.com%2Fasset%2F6645075e220000340026db1d.jpeg%3Fops%3D1200_630%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2